description: Boris Johnson is promising a big trade deal in 2020 but the EU Commission chief had a warning for him.
title: Why Brexit Stage Two may turn into a rocky ride
title_page: Why Brexit Stage Two may turn into a rocky ride - BBC News
maintext: By the end of this month, both the European and the UK parliaments will have ratified a negotiated divorce deal. As of 1 February, the UK will no longer be an EU member and by the year's end, says Boris Johnson, an ambitious new trade deal will have been negotiated and signed off by both sides.
